727626f.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 192nd Street
727626f.text:
Northern Boulevard (foreground), south side, at 192nd
Street, viewing southeastward across the former Bowden
property (1891) and showing new real estate development.
The cottage is at the S.E. corner of the intersection.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS

727627f-b.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 192nd Street
727627f-b.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, between 192nd and 193rd
Streets. The frame bungalow is the Auburndale Real Estate
Center ofTice .
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
